{"tid":1275281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把心愛的立法會打碎了","createTime":"2019-07-01T18:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:22:28.000Z","uid":53369,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4aa287a8c319ee2f2441bce733024ad03905e9","tid":1275281,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:51:36.000Z","msg":"今天不小心把心愛的立法會打碎了 <br />\n事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞 <br />\n發現打碎了的玻璃碎 <br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方 <br />\n再為其拍照<br />\n<br />\n這短短的三十分鐘 <br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間 <br />\n打碎了的立法會<br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西 <br />\n而那立法會開閘的那一聲 <br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音<br />\n<br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情 <br />\n也未必是最糟 <br />\n因為最糟的 <br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現 <br />\n又或者根本就是自己 <br />\n我想我找到了答案"},{"pid":"bba2f9613d763ee18b49e40709ce341b83701f42","tid":1275281,"uid":52477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1f39376399dd309364d3892ec3539b87809f90","tid":1275281,"uid":53369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bba2f9613d763ee18b49e40709ce341b83701f42","tid":1275281,"uid":52477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:53:20.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:55:56.000Z","msg":"見到有人講返d人譴責前線打爆玻璃<br />\n一講起爆玻璃就諗起呢篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1e3fd0329d9f177f59c75d